		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">寻捕械推出一个排满尖牙的排斥装甲，造成<span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="432" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">寻捕械朝天发射一束高能脉冲，其持续打击地面，持续造成<span color="#ff9999">70%,35%,14%,7%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">寻捕械朝玩家发射连续的集中热能激光，持续造成<span color="#ff9999">60%</span><span>伤害，至多3次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，寻捕械突然朝玩家发动赤牙合击，造成<span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「应战对策」充满后，寻捕械会发射持续5s的集束激光，持续造成<span color="#ff9999">100%,10%</span><span>伤害，期间抗性恢复正常。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
